author: Just Jared
title: 10 Times Beyonce Stopped The World - From Pregnancies to Surprise Albums!
text:
Beyonce just threw the Internet into chaos by announcing she is pregnant with twins , but this isn’t the first time she’s stopped the world! 
The 35-year-old superstar has captured the attention of millions many times over the course of career! 
From her first pregnancy announcement during the 2011 MTV VMAs to the surprise debut of both Lemonade and her self-titled album, she’s practically got this down to a science! 
We’ve gathered some of Beyonce ‘s best moments that have totally brought the world to a halt. 
Click through the slideshow to see 10 moments Beyonce stopped the world… Just Jared on Facebook
